OL,3,COwen Cooper sweeps RTS Awards for
OL,4,CNetflix drama Adolescence
OL,6,FAdolescence star Owen Cooper has
OL,7,Fcontinued his remarkable awards season
OL,8,Frun by taking home two Royal
OL,9,FTelevision Awards (RTS) for his role
OL,10,Fin the Netflix series.
OL,12,FThe 16-year-old dominated the 2026
OL,13,Fawards ceremony in London, cementing
OL,14,Fhis status as one of the biggest up-
OL,15,Fand-coming actors in the industry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
