OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774461963
OL,3,COwen Cooper sweeps RTS Awards for
OL,4,CNetflix drama Adolescence
OL,6,FCooper, who is originally from
OL,7,FWarrington, Cheshire, walked away with
OL,8,Ftwo of the evening's most prestigious
OL,9,Fhonours: the Breakthrough Award and
OL,10,FBest Supporting Actor in the male
OL,11,Fcategory.
OL,13,FHis double win comes on the heels of a
OL,14,Fmassive year for the young star, who
OL,15,Fhas already added an Emmy and a Golden
OL,16,FGlobe to his trophy cabinet for the
OL,17,Fsame role.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
