OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1774461963
OL,3,COwen Cooper sweeps RTS Awards for
OL,4,CNetflix drama Adolescence
OL,6,F"This was work that showed total
OL,7,Fconviction from a natural talent," the
OL,8,Fjudges said of Cooper's performance.
OL,9,F"A performance of phenomenal skill in
OL,10,Fa demanding, uncompromising role."
OL,12,FThe four-part drama, which has been
OL,13,Fnominated for 11 Baftas, gripped
OL,14,Faudiences and critics since its
OL,15,Frelease, following the story of 13-
OL,16,Fyear-old Jamie Miller, a schoolboy
OL,17,Farrested for the murder of a teenage
OL,18,Fgirl.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@bO]qD@AOUrD@bO]
